course_title: Pediatric Acute Care NP Practicum III
course_description: This course continues to elaborate on acute care of children that are acutely or chronically ill. Emphasis is on the delivery, analysis, and evaluation of health care in an inpatient acute care setting.
prerequisites: Only EOHMPH, EOHIHMPH, and EOHEPIMPH students have permission to enroll in this course.
